reviewText: I sometimes like movies that are not the usual story line - enjoyed the twists and turns - foosball is a fun game.

I'm sorry to have discontinued this video download, but you can still watch the movie. Just visit the film's site for more information.

Eduardo Soto-Falcon, director and producer

This is a pretty good movie. I found it entertaining, if you like short films...you'll like this! You should check it out!

Tim Rozon plays Duke who tries to charm an unexpecting stranger that shows up at a fooseball tourney on accident with her boyfriend.

(Promotional video and trailer of the film.) (UPDATED) This download still seems to work, even though I asked Amazon to cancel it. Anyway, I got another DVD and digital download provider who has a more reasonable price and apparently will honor my royalties. And most importantly, it's an improved master. Please visit [...]. Eduardo Soto-Falcon, director and producer
